comments: Randle (NYK) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Barrett (NYK) and Wagner (ORL) mutually engage and disengage in marginal contact off-ball as the screen is being set.
Carter Jr. (ORL) places his hands momentarily to Barrett's (NYK) side and then rolls to the basket.
Carter Jr. (ORL) briefly grasps Sims' (NYK) arm and immediately releases it as he positions himself in the paint to receive the ball.
Carter Jr. (ORL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Carter Jr. (ORL) moves alongside Brunson's (NYK) path and maintains a legal guarding position while he contests the driving shot attempt.
Brunson (NYK) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes two steps before passing the ball.
Carter Jr. (ORL) firms up in Grimes' (NYK) path as the pick is being set.
Randle (NYK) has his arm slightly extended forward as Wagner (ORL) moves into his space and some contact occurs.
Harris (ORL) commits a personal take foul against Brunson (NYK).
Brunson (NYK) commits a personal take foul against Fultz (ORL).
Wagner (ORL) commits a personal take foul against Brunson (NYK).
Barrett (NYK) commits a personal take foul against Banchero (ORL).
Carter Jr. (ORL) commits a personal take foul against Randle (NYK).
